 * is not suitable for high number of tweens/performance test
 * as nothing is strong typed for smallness sake. 
 * Use twin instead who is strong typed
 * 
 * 		autorotate /
 * 		sound / 
 * 		tint /
 * 		text /
 * 		textColor /
 * 		hexcolor /
